{"tid":1232601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毅進制 警方料除夕有30萬人維港賞煙花","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T19:06:54.000Z","uid":83487,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9c294a9ed27abbefcb34940a13be72d21326eb24","tid":1232601,"uid":83487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"警方料除夕有30萬人維港賞煙花 <br />\n時事脈搏 | 2018年12月28日  <br />\n<br />\n旅發局除夕夜將在維港舉行煙火滙演，警方預計，當晚約有30萬人在維港兩岸觀賞煙花，與去年相若，警方當天下午開始會在九龍及港島多處地方，進行分階段封路措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec1ec65f10b285bfe8645727d6f5bc810f4fd25","tid":1232601,"uid":83487,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWKQ6Gd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWKQ6Gd.png&h=da98bf03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n30萬人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbSfymd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbSfymd.png&h=fcdd4b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n33.8萬人"},{"pid":"e7912db635afd5512b6c144044fbc711ccf722d5","tid":1232601,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d398705a92e9ed92f089bd05649daacfae35ea8b","tid":1232601,"uid":47380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98aee12d3ad9abae66eb2430edb5c06f78b53c7","tid":1232601,"uid":51583,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"dec1ec65f10b285bfe8645727d6f5bc810f4fd25","tid":1232601,"uid":83487,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"